Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.radio

Class RadioServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.AbstractComponentService<RadioComponentType,Radio>
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.radio.RadioServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
RadioService, Insertion
public class RadioServiceImpl extends AbstractComponentService<RadioComponentType,Radio> implements RadioService
Implementation of the RadioService interface, providing methods to select radio buttons, verify their state (enabled, selected, visible), and retrieve their text values. Extends AbstractComponentService to manage creation and retrieval of Radio instances.

This class delegates core functionality to an internally retrieved Radio instance, created for each specified RadioComponentType. Methods conform to the RadioService contract, ensuring a uniform approach to handling radio buttons across various UI designs.

All public methods handle operations such as checking button states, locating elements by container or locator, and selecting them by text or strategy. The insertion method also implements the Insertion interface for data insertion scenarios.
